footer.moreInfosText:
OPSMAP waxay ujeedadeedu tahay inay siiso hawl wadeenada samafalka xal u saamaxaya inay ku soo koobaan gobolka adeegyada ka dhex jira goobaha kala duwan ee lagu martiqaado barakacayaasha. Adigoo si otomaatig ah u soo saaraya "astaamaha goobta", OPSMAPs waxay u oggolaaneysaa hawl wadeenada samafalka inay si dhakhso leh u helaan dulmar guud oo ku saabsan macluumaadka lagama maarmaanka u ah maareynta goobta. Isticmaalayaashu waxay si fudud uga heli karaan macluumaadka iyagoo adeegsanaya shabakadda internetka ( dashboard ), oo u istcimaal si ay u aqoonsadaan qodobbada u baahan tallaabo deg deg ah. Laba nooc oo OPSMAP ah ayaa la heli karaa: nooc "caadiga ah" iyo nooca "caado".
Nooca caadiga ah waa xalka isha furan, oo ay soo saartay CartONG sanadkii 2021, iyada oo la kaashanayo qaybta UNHCR GDS (Liisanka MIT, nooca hadda ah: {version}). Sawirro la adeegsaday ayaa ka yimid "Astaamaha bina-aadamnimada" keydka macluumaadka ( Credit OCHA, oo shati ka hoosaysa CC BY 3.0 )
